net.tridentsdk.server.data

Class RecordBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.tridentsdk.server.data.RecordBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Writable

    public class RecordBuilder
extends Object
implements Writable
    Records the state of a block as it was when the snapshot was taken

    Note that this may not always represent the most accurate view of the block in question.

    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
